ntent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aeh1719926275572.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aeh1719926275572.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aeh1719926275572.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ama1665702634609\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n trigger columnSorted \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ama1665702634609__trigger_columnsorted_393212\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Interactive trigger that handles processing when the user clicks a column header in the list view of a Tree widget, thereby sorting the list view according to that column, in ascending or descending order.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ama1665702634609__topic_d116840e1_d116841e1_d116842e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104aeh1719926275572_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ama1665702634609__codeblock_oxf_km5_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">   trigger columnSorted\n   params\n      numeric columnid : in\n      string sortingorder : in ; ASC | DESC\n   endparams\n\n   <var class=\"keyword varname\">; &lt;Your code here&gt;</var>\n   end ; trigger columnSorted\n         </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ama1665702634609__section_w1638ab1b7b5_w1639ab1b7_w1640ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ama1665702634609__table_d14396e1_d14397e1_d14398e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated when the user clicks a column header in the list view, thereby sorting the list view according to that column, in ascending or descending order.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ama1665702634609__topic_d83007e1_d83008e1_d83009e1_d83010e1_d83011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395590e131\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ama1665702634609__li_d44456e1_d44457e1_d44458e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">columnid</span>—column number in the list view, counting from 1\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ama1665702634609__li_d44459e1_d44460e1_d44461e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">sortingorder</span>—one of:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ama1665702634609__li_d44462e1_d44463e1_d44464e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ASC</code>—ascending\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ama1665702634609__li_d44465e1_d44466e1_d44467e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DESC</code>—descending\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419421\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419421\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger columnSorted Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger columnSorted Interactive trigger that handles processing when the user clicks a column header in the list view of a Tree widget, thereby sorting the list view according to that column, in ascending or descending order. Explain this code trigger columnSorted params numeric columnid : in string sortingorder : in ; ASC | DESC endparams ; <Your code here> end ; trigger columnSorted Copy Applies to: Form widgets: utree (Tree) Activation: Activated when the user clicks a column header in the list view, thereby sorting the list view according to that column, in ascending or descending order. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Parameters columnid —column number in the list view, counting from 1 sortingorder —one of: ASC —ascending DESC —descending Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}